high_descs: turn around and walk over to the toilet on the left side of the room
grab a candle off of the top of the toilet
turn around and walk over to the right side of the green cabinet ahead
place the candle in a drawer on the right side of the cabinet
turn around and walk back over to the toilet ahead
grab another candle off of the toilet
turn around and walk over to the right side of the green cabinet again
place the candle in the same part of the cabinet you put the other candle in
anns.task_desc: place two candles inside of the green bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and go to the toilet.
Pick up a candle from the toilet.
Return to the counter behind you.
Open the bottom right drawer and put the candle inside.
Return to the toilet behind you.
Pick up a candle from the toilet.
Return to the counter behind you.
Open the bottom right drawer and put the candle inside.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles from the toilet to a drawer.

high_descs: Turn to the right, head towards the tub, then turn right and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the far side of the toilet.
Turn around and head to the counter.
Open the bottom right drawer and put the candle in, then shut the drawer.
Turn around and head to the toilet.
Pick up the candle by the soap.
Turn around and head to the counter.
Open the bottom right drawer and put the candle in, then shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put the candles on the toilet in the bottom right drawer below the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the back of the toilet that is behind the bar of soap.
Turn around and head back to the counter
Open the bottom right drawer and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
Turn around and go back to the toilet.
Pick up the candle that is on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and head back to the counter.
Open the bottom right drawer, put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two candles in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn and go to the side of the toilet.  The opposite side of the toilet paper holder.
Grab the candle that is behind the bar of soap off the back of the toilet.
With the candle in hand go to the cabinet with the green drawers.
Put the candle in the second drawer down in the drawer on the right. Shut the drawer.
Turn and go to the toilet on the side opposite of the toilet paper holder.
Pick up the candle that is on the back of the toilet.
With the candle in hand go to the green cabinet.
Put the candle in the second drawer all the way on the right. To the right of the other candle that is in there.
